display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> a Noetherian subring of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {R}]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A\otimes \mathbb {Q}]]></fr:tex> is a field.
    The useful cases are <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A=\mathbb {Z}]]></fr:tex>, <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {Q}]]></fr:tex>, or <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {R}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
